Package: malan
Type: Package
Title: MAle Lineage ANalysis
Version: 0.0.3.1
Date: 2018-04-17
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Mikkel Meyer", family = "Andersen", 
        email = "mikl@math.aau.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Author: Mikkel Meyer Andersen <mikl@math.aau.dk>
Maintainer: Mikkel Meyer Andersen <mikl@math.aau.dk>
Description: MAle Lineage ANlysis by simulating genealogies backwards and imposing short tandem repeats (STR) mutations forwards. Intended for forensic Y chromosomal STR (Y-STR) haplotype analyses. Numerous analyses are possible, e.g. number of matches and meiotic distance to matches.
